summary: Rudolf EDMOND NOBLE was born on July 8, 1933 in Ince, California. He graduated from University of California, Berkeley ‘california’ with a B.S. inorganic Chemistry in 1953. In 1963 he completed a Ph.D. at Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio.
